graph LR
    KubeRay[KubeRay Operator]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|runtime platform| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.26+]
    KubeRay -->|distributed computing| Ray[Ray Framework 2.0+]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional/Conditional)
    KubeRay -->|TLS certificates| CertManager[cert-manager 1.11+]
    KubeRay -->|OpenShift features| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.12+]
    KubeRay -->|advanced routing| GatewayAPI[Gateway API v1/v1beta1]
    KubeRay -.->|metrics collection| Prometheus[Prometheus]
    KubeRay -.->|GCS FT storage| ExternalRedis[External Redis 6.0+]

    %% OpenShift sub-components
    OpenShift -->|authentication| OAuthServer[OAuth Server]
    OpenShift -->|external access| Routes[Route API]
    OpenShift -->|TLS certs| ServiceCA[Service CA]
    OpenShift -->|pod security| SCC[SecurityContextConstraints]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies
    RHOAIOperator[RHOAI Operator] -->|deploys & configures| KubeRay
    KubeRay -.->|batch scheduling| Kueue[Kueue - optional]
    KubeRay -.->|authorization| Authorino[Authorino - future]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| KubeRay
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|auto-deploy models| KubeRay

    %% External Services
    KubeRay -->|pull images| Registry[Container Registry<br/>quay.io, registry.redhat.io]
    KubeRay -->|API operations| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

    %% Data flow
    Ray -->|runs in| RayPods[Ray Head/Worker Pods]
    RayPods -->|managed by| KubeRay

